featured_reviews.review_id: Best Masjid in Rourkela. I found it very peaceful place, the people there are very friendly including Shaykh. Shaykh is very knowledgeable you can get the solution of every masail from him. Masjid contains various hadith collection from Bukhari to Tafsir Ibn Kathir in different languages which most of the mosque lack. Whenever I am free I feel free to go to mosque so that i can perform salah and read quran with tafsir . My personal favorite work is to go and explore more about my deen by reading Sahih Bukari, Muslim Abu dawood and Tafsir Ibn Kathir.
